    "updated_at": "2020-05-10T00:37:22Z",
    "body": "Some negative experience with linking CRT objects manually instead of relying on gcc on musl targets:\r\nhttps://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/40113#issuecomment-311049045\r\nhttps://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/40113#issuecomment-311049710\r\n\r\nSo, musl experience repeats the mingw one - using system CRT objects and libraries is strongly preferable to using those shipped with rustc.\r\n",
